title: Charming,Manicured,Clean,2Br.1Ba.Unit in Historical DowntownSta.Clara
posting_body: ['$2750/mo.', 'with 1 yr.', 'Lease.', '800Sq.', 'Ft. 2Br./1Ba. unit in Duplex.', 'Charming, Clean, Hardwood Floors, Washer/Dryer.', 'Off-street parking.', 'Available for 8/1/2022 Move In Date.', 'Duplex is located in Quiet, Safe, Highly Desirable, Historical, Santa Clara neighborhood.', 'Beautiful, Peaceful setting.', 'Gardener Included.', 'Convenient to all transportation, schools, churches, parks, senior center, recreational areas, farmers markets, and (valley fair) shopping.', ' (Few Blocks from Santa Clara University.)', 'A Must SEE!', 'Owner will be holding OPEN HOUSE This Weekend 1-2pm and/or by Appointment Only.', 'CALL TODAY!!', 'show contact info', '.', 'Please Call', 'show contact info', '(M-F, between hours of 9-5pm) to set up a viewing time.', 'Please DO NOT DISTURB OCCUPANTS.', 'Rent is $2750 with a 1 year lease.', 'In order to secure unit, applicant must provide:', '1.', '  Completed Applications', '2.', '  1st Mo.', 'Security Deposit (NOT to be used as Last Months Rent.)', '3.', '  All Applicants must pay for and PASS Credit Check.', '4.', '  References Requested.', '5.', '  Owner will only be available to show on weekends and possibly evenings, so please call to make appointment at:', 'show contact info', '.', ' Please leave a Clear Message with your phone number and Name (spelled phonetically) and we will', 'return you call.']
